reviewText: John Oates is incredible as a single artist and this dvd proves it!  Still incredibly sexy as well!  WOOF!
A great album, a complete reflection of the John Oates style.... cajon rock...
The Finest writing, perfection is beyond and beyond EXCELLANT. Buy this CD. Please give us a LP Album. Please?
Great, Terrific both video and CD.  One of his best ever!  *****
good interviews, performing is good but not very active
Fabulous.  Saw the concert on Palladium and very pleased with this set that includes both CD with bonus tracks and DVD.  You'll get up and dance, then lay back and cruise.

I caught John Oates on Paladia (now called MTV Live) and was incredibly hooked.  I listed to Hall and Oates when younger and while I enjoyed them a ton then, this is a completely new sound than that time.

This is an awesome DVD!!  I'm incredibly hooked on the sound and the setting of the recorded sessions!!  Wish I could catch him live.  This video shows a more intimate picture of John!!
The best in years great idea for a gift all classic oldies!
Wow nice album. John Oats at his best.

I bought this for my husband, but I really love it also. The music is beautiful and it is interesting to see a glimpse of Mr. Oates life. The set was not expensive at all. Great buy. Very glad we added it to our collection.
Saw the video on Palladium. CD contains tracks not included on video. Good video and CD.
This dvd is absolutely great listening. Good blend of music.
